title: Ep. - 250 - Ian Gelfand, Producer of RHOD, Summer House and Family Karma Luke Gulbranson from Summer House
description:
Ian Gelfand has been Executive Producer of several reality television show hits including Real Housewives of Dallas, Summer House, and Family Karma. He talks about what three elements make for a great show, behind the scenes of some of RHOD and Summer House’s funniest moments, and more.

 

Luke Gulbranson from Summer House talks about how he was cast for the show, his relationship with Hannah, and what he really thinks about Jules.

 

 Reality Life with Kate Casey
